timelineItems.desc: The Portland Timbers return home to face a huge test in their aim to start moving up the Western Conference when they take Eastern Conference leaders D.C. United on Wednesday evening at Providence Park.
timelineItems.title: HIGHLIGHTS: Portland Timbers vs D.C. United | May 27, 2015

timelineItems.text: #PORvDC team news: Johnson features in starting XI for first time since injury; Olsen rests most starters for long midweek trip #MLS
